  "title": { "rendered": "Areas of Expertise" },
  "content": {
    "rendered": "<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/3&#8243;][vc_column_text]Choosing the right legal counsel can be one of the most difficult obstacles. You deserve someone who has extensive experience, common sense, diversified knowledge, and understands complex legal issues. Our attorneys are trustworthy, honest, have the utmost integrity, and truly care about helping our clients. Our firm has a sincere appreciation for our client&#8217;s troubles and concerns and will take the time to listen and understand.<\/p>\n<p>This law firm specializes in a wide range of areas of expertise in the law. Given our extensive legal knowledge, we are able to navigate our clients through multiple legal issues while building lasting relationships. We are equipped with lawyers who can help a client form or start a business; prepare their employment contracts, manuals, and personnel policies; negotiate and prepare contracts; and pursue or defend lawsuits for our clients. We have lawyers who have sat on the defense side of lawsuits as well as on the plaintiff&#8217;s side allowing us to outsmart and outmaneuver the opposition.<\/p>\n<p>Below is a list\u00a0of the practice areas that we cover with a corresponding web link for more information:[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;8405&#8243; img_size=&#8221;large&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; offset=&#8221;vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-138\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/los-angeles-business-law-attorney-corporate-law-firm\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Business Law<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-137\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/civil-litigation\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Civil Litigation<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-3645\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/contract-drafting-negotiating-attorney-law-firm-services\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Contract Drafting <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-3667\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/debt-collection-attorneys-los-angeles-ventura-county\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Debt Collection<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;50&#8243;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; offset=&#8221;vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-3667\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/real-estate-lawyer-los-angeles\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Real Estate<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-136\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/employment-law-attorneys-los-angeles-ventura-county\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Employment Law<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-133\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/intellectual-property\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Intellectual Property<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-1168\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/unfair-business-practices-attorney-california-law-firm\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Unfair Business Practices<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;50&#8243;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; offset=&#8221;vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-132\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/fraud-attorney-services-in-los-angeles-ventura-county\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Fraud<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-1153\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/lawyer-for-wills-trusts-los-angeles-ventura-ca\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Wills &amp; Trusts<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-135\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/personal-injury-attorney-los-angeles-ca\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Personal Injury<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<li id=\"nav-menu-item-3639\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page \"><strong><span style=\"color: #353c4e;\"><a class=\"\" style=\"color: #353c4e;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/wrongful-death-lawyer-in-los-angeles-ventura-ca\/\"><span class=\"item_outer\"><span class=\"item_inner\"><span class=\"item_text\">Wrongful Death<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;50&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/business-law\/\">Corporate\/Business Law<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/legal-expertise\/civil-litigation\/\">Civil Litigation<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/legal-expertise\/employment-law\/\">Employment Law<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/estate-planning\/\">Estate Planning\/Wills &amp; Trusts<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/personal-injury\/\">Personal Injury\/Wrongful Death<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/legal-expertise\/real-estate-transactions\/\">Real Estate Transactions<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/legal-expertise\/intellectual-property\/\">Intellectual Property<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/legal-expertise\/fraud\/\">Fraud<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #000080;\" href=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/areas-of-expertise\/unlawful-business-practices\/\">Unfair Competition\/Unlawful Business Practices<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;50&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>",
